full_text:
真相としては先月 #nflverse ネタの時にフォロー受けてフォロバしたがすぐ外されました
フォロー継続してましたが試合中のネタかマジかわからないanalyticsTweetがTL上出るのがノイズだったので私も外しました
まだ私に対する批判Tweetの方が見てられます、ちなみに最近再フォローされたのも知ってます

Puntpdate, week 12!

🦵top of the list starting to take shape - could be quite the race for P1
🦵Morstead is back baybee (he'll keep showing up with a Jets logo for a bit bc that's where the majority of his punts have been)

#nflverse https://t.co/v332dbZPmb

This updated version adds transparency to the field and to non-scoring drives. Only scoring drives end in a white point. Also added time of possession and number of plays. Still work in progress. 
#nflverse https://t.co/8L4rVSv42U

Update Week 13
Data: #nflverse
#rstats https://t.co/PKn6s0Bxlr

Wanted to throw together a shiny app to keep up with the pass depth each week. Will try to make sure it stays working! 
https://t.co/ifP3u02IN0
#nflfastr #rstats #nflverse

Is there any explanation for why MIN is so so bad when leading? It comes back to bite them every week and (aside from noise of a small sample?) I don't see an easy explanation for why this is the case. Any ideas?
#nflverse https://t.co/CFb7SXYDS3

Yes, the Chiefs have won a bunch recently, but looking past W/L record it has to be concerning that 4 of Mahomes's 5 worst career EPA games have come recently. Could he turn it around? Ofc. But as a Mahomes Stan(and ik I'm not alone) maybe it is time to adjust priors🤷‍♂️ 
#nflverse https://t.co/MJMpowmsQQ

@nflfastR has an xYAC model with which we can calculate Air EPA + xYAC EPA. I do that for completions and leave incompletions' EPA untouched. Interceptions are also untouched (no xYAC for the return). This is the result:

#nflverse https://t.co/rRm1re81xw https://t.co/9n24l6XV1X

Saquon Barkley is the Jameis Winston of Running Backs.

Since entering the league, he ranks 3rd in percentage of runs over 20 yards, but 2nd in percentage of runs below 0 yards.

Like @Danny_Heifetz says, on every play, Saquon either hits a home run or strikes out.

#nflverse https://t.co/W5YgTxmCch

A preview infographic for the huge Pats-Bills showdown this week:
🏈 #BillsMafia have been better on offense and defense, but Pats are on a hot streak
🏈 Mac-Allen QB Battle will define the game
🏈 AFC East lead at stake

Data: #nflverse | Inspiration: @bestballstats https://t.co/AOKMxSeL9c

the bills and patriots are leading the league in how much garbage time they play in this year #nflverse https://t.co/kPp93rbWZ5
#nflverse https://t.co/fjBS1px1Uq
https://t.co/1FeWUqqhUq and the #nflverse game data have been updated to reflect these changes. https://t.co/NOXJhlIWrB

Things got hectic and I completely forgot to post my model's #nfl picks and projections yesterday.  So, without further ado...the model's current projections #nflverse https://t.co/2zq0HRlbTr https://t.co/HNGzKzkIFS

And the model's Week 13 picks (fixing my code error MAY have corresponded with a week in which the model outperformed both @FiveThirtyEight and @LeeSharpeNFL prediction market 🤔) #nflverse https://t.co/tibw2V7krd

With only three pass attempts, the Patriots recorded a -56.7% pass rate over expectation, the lowest-recorded PROE in the @nflfastR era (since 1999). The previous low was -44.9%, set last year in Week 12 by the Broncos when they didn't have any eligible QBs. #nflverse

How much has each team gotten out of their top six selections from the 2021 draft so far?

Data: #nflverse https://t.co/OWZ9bBUdPK

The people have been clamoring for hourly QB rankings. Here they are!

Rankings are based on https://t.co/ozHHxdbN9b's EPA+CPOE composite index.

#nflverse https://t.co/UUXcLc22JK

New graph! I thought I might try to visualize how many snaps each team's preseason offensive starters (+2 more skill players) have played in 2021

Week 1 is the left-most column and the most recent game is on the far right. Darker tiles = more snaps. X = inactive

Data: #nflverse https://t.co/XSNtxNRTuU

Okay guys, I think it's time to retire. 
(X-axis at different scales)
Data: #nflverse

#KeepPounding #SteelersNation https://t.co/lYQX514hrF

This sunday we had two QBs making the best game of their career by EPA/play!
Kyler Murray and, yes, Garder Minshew!
#RedSea  #FlyEaglesFly
